Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Course
    This class makes a course object that will let courses be created.
    CourseBag
    This class stores course Object into an arrayList so that information can be stored and found.
    Faculty
    This class creates a Faculty object.
    FacultyBag
    This class will create an ArrayList for caulty objects to be stored
    Major
    This class creates a major.
    MajorBag
    This Class will store Major objects into an arrayList that can be saved and loaded when the user wants.
    Person
    The person creates a person with information that can be stored about the person.
    Student
    The student class inherits from person and also adds arrayList of all the course that are required to achieve its major.
    StudentBag
    Student Bag class will store all the student objects created into an Array List that can be saved and read from.
